{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, with 2-shot demonstration as the fair setting, we state the claim that \"Few-Shot-CoT does not consistently improve overall performance\".",
    "Claim on \"Risk Awareness\".",
    "The reasons why we conduct qualitative analysis rather than quantitative analysis are as follows.",
    "Due to the underexplored principles of knowledge and reasoning capability of LLMs in community, quantitative analysis may introduce uncertainty and uninterpretability that can not be accomodated in one paper.",
    "It is basically acknowledged that reasoning is an emergent ability of LLMs that came out of amassing knowledge (Wei et al., 2022a)."
  ]
}